        [32m'Methods prose. This implicitly closes everything still open at greater depth.\n'[39m +
        [32m'\n'[39m +
        [32m'Features: full three-level nesting, with implicit closing at all depths handled by the section-nesting plugin.\n'[39m +
        [32m'\n'[39m +
        [32m'### 5.4. Section title vocabulary\n'[39m +
